title: Neto's Sausage Co., Inc. Recalls Meat and Poultry Products Produced Without Benefit of Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, Jan. 6, 2015 Netos Sausage Co., Inc, a Santa Clara, Calif., establishment, is recalling approximately 7,687 pounds of beef, pork, and chicken products that were produced and labeled with the federal mark of inspection without the benefit of FSIS inspection, the U.S. Department of...
